data.description: Lake Catherine Home! Imagine winding down your days with a soothing sunset boat ride, or entertaining friends and family lakeside. The spacious deck and landscaped grounds provide a perfect backdrop for any gathering or a tranquil spot to escape and enjoy your lakeside retreat. This home lets you enjoy the abundance of natural light with the large insulated windows. The Kitchen and Bathrooms have been updated; Fresh Paint Inside & Out; New Roof 2024; New Deck; New MiniSplit in Family Room; and a Gazebo.  Come enjoy living in this beautiful home designed for peace and relaxation on a cove of Lake Catherine in Lakeside School District.  (See Agent Remarks)
